<concept id="concept_B32294CC9FA643A2A14A74B1DAA49C95" xml:lang="en-us">
    <title>Creating a Self-Signed Domain Certificate </title>
    <conbody>
        <section>
            <p>To create a self-signed certificate for the application server domain where <ph
                    conref="../../Shared/Product_Name.xml#ProductNameTopic/Product_Abbr"
                /> has been deployed, execute the following command of the JRE you are using: </p>
            <p>
                <codeblock>&lt;YourJRE&gt;/bin/keytool –genkey –alias s1as –keysize 1024 
 –keystore keystore.jks</codeblock>
            </p>
        </section>
        <section> </section>
    </conbody>
</concept>
